GH QUALITY CONSTRUCTION – The Tooltreaux twist drill bits are made of high-speed, durable stainless steel that won’t rust. Stainless steel is a great material for drill bits because it’s heat and abrasion resistant, ensuring your bits stand the test of time.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">CUTS HOLES ACCURATELY – Our drill bits are stable and won’t easily break. They are designed to cut holes quickly, accurately and safely in metal and other materials. The twist drill bits spiral with ease and conveniently remove debris from the hole so you can accomplish your project in a timely manner!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">MULTI-PURPOSE TOOLS – The high-speed drill bits can be used on a number of materials including cast iron, high-temperature alloy plastics, hard plastics, stainless steel, titanium alloy, woods and other soft materials. These are must-have hobby tool essentials for metal-smithing, metalworking and drilling!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">VARIETY OF SIZES – Our set comes with a variety of drill sizes, ranging from 1.05mm to 2mm. They all feature a universal round drill shank of 3/32”  and will fit drills with a 1/16” shaft. Sizes included: 1.05mm, 1.1mm, 1.15mm, 1.2mm, 1.25mm, 1.3mm, 1.4mm, 1.45mm, 1.5mm, 1.6mm, 1.7mm, 1.8mm, 1.9mm, 2mm</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMPACT AND PORTABLE – The twist drill set comes with a black PVC pouch bag that will keep the drills organized when not in use. The pouch is easily foldable so you can store them in your tool box, workshop or travel bag.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>Tooltreaux High Speed Stainless Steel Drill Bits Set 1.05 to 2mm 15 Pieces</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">14.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Whether you’re a metalworking novice or a drilling expert, you’ll need a good, high-quality set of twist drill bits for home improvement and hobby craft projects. The ToolTreaux 15pc Drill Bit Set comes with 15 twist drill bits, ranging in size from 1.05mm to 2mm.\n\nOur drill bits are made of durable, strong stainless steel that won’t rust. Stainless steel is an ideal material for drill bits because it his heat and abrasion-resistant, ensuring that your drill bits will stand the test of time.\n\nThe ToolTreaux drill bits are stable and will not easily break. They are designed to cut holes quickly, accurately, and safely in metals and other materials The twist drill bits spiral with ease and conveniently remove debris from the hole so you can accomplish your project in a timely manner!\n\nThese high-speed drill bits can be used on a number of materials including cast iron, high-temperature alloy plastics, hard plastics, stainless steel, titanium alloy, wood, and other soft materials. These are must-have hobby tool essentials for metal-smithing, metalworking, and drilling! \n\nThe drill comes with a convenient black PVC pouch so you can store and organize them when not in use. The pouch can be folded and tucked away into your toolbox, workshop, or travel bag. Make sure to grab a set of these drill bits before your next home improvement or hobby project!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t<table>&nbsp;</table>\n\t</div>\n</body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
